## Node name and cookie are set by env.sh.eex via RELEASE_NODE / RELEASE_COOKIE.
## Do NOT set -sname/-name or -setcookie here.

## Increase distribution buffer for large inter-node messages (32MB).
+zdbbl 32768

## Net tick time (seconds). Nodes unresponsive for 4x this are considered down.
-kernel net_ticktime 15

## Enable kernel poll (epoll/kqueue) for better I/O scaling.
+K true

## Async thread pool for file I/O in the tool system.
+A 16
